data.description: Discover this remarkable, one-story gem that's as unique as it is beautiful! Nestled on an expansive lot, this home boasts a myriad of luxurious upgrades. From gleaming granite countertops in the kitchen and bathrooms to elegant laminate and tile flooring, energy-efficient double-paned windows to exquisite wood beams and high ceilings, you'll be enchanted by every corner. Step outside to a relaxing deck and covered back patio, surrounded by meticulously crafted custom landscaping. Don't let this opportunity slip by – explore this property in a wonderfully maintained neighborhood, within the coveted Klein ISD zone.
